---

<section class="relative bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-50 via-orange-50 to-amber-50 py-20 md:py-32 overflow-hidden">
	<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
		<div class="absolute w-96 h-96 bg-amber-300 rounded-full -top-48 -right-48"></div>
		<div class="absolute w-96 h-96 bg-orange-300 rounded-full -bottom-48 -left-48"></div>
	</div>
	
	<div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
		<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 leading-tight">
				Transforma tus Espacios<br />
				<span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-600 to-orange-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
					con Estilo
				</span>
			</h1>
			<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
				Descubre nuestra exclusiva colección de cerámicas y porcelanatos de alta calidad, perfectos para cualquier ambiente
			</p>
			<a
				href="#catalogo"
				class="inline-block bg-amber-600 hover:bg-amber-700 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-200 transform hover:scale-105 active:scale-95"
			>
				Ver Catálogo
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-16 bg-gradient-to-t from-white to-transparent"></div>
</section>
